            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi eterni dei amen. Anno nativitate
                        eius millesimo centesimo et optuagesimo nono, settimo kal. aplelis,
                        indictione settima. Ex huius instrumenti pateat recitatione quod nos
                                <persName><name ref="Anconevolio">Ancondevolius</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Wadardus">Guadardus</name></persName> germani
                        et quondam <persName><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName> in
                        comutatione dare et tradere videmur tibi <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildibrandus</name></persName>, custos et rector <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >ospitalis</rs> de <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                                >Altepascio</placeName></orgName>, duas terrarum petias que sunt
                        posite in plagis et finibus Putei. Prima in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210">Cafagio</placeName>. Que tenet ambo capita in <rs
                            key="#Roads">viis puplicis</rs>. Unum laterum tenet in terra dicti
                        ospitalis, aliud tenet in terra <persName><name ref="Corsus"
                            >Corsi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannis</name></persName> et in terra quam detinet <persName><name
                                ref="Amatus">Amatus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Guittus">Ghitti</name></persName>. Que est ad iustam mensuratam
                        perticam stariora quatuor. Secunda tenet unum caput in via pupliga, aliud
                        cum uno latere tenet in terra <persName ref="#people/3217"
                            >Aldimari</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3218"
                            >Alberti</persName>, aliud lato tenet in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Iolicta">Iolette</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Hubertellus">Ubertelli</name></persName>. Que terre petia est
                        stariors quatuor et medietas unius panori. (…) Pro qua nostra comutatione
                        recipimus a te dicto Ildibladus retore una terre petiam que est posita in
                        plagis et finibus <placeName key="#Roads" ref="#places/63">Sancte Marie
                            Montis</placeName> seu in loco ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/63"
                            >Via Maiore</placeName>. Que tenet unum caput in terra filiorum quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Brunicardus">Bronicardi</name></persName>,
                        aliud tenet in terra <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannis</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Beatus">Beatique</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Berta Plandingi">Berte Plandingi</name></persName>. Unum
                        laterum in terra <persName><name ref="Guerrus">Gueri</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Sigeroctus">Sigerocti</name></persName>, aliud
                        in terra quam detinet <persName><name ref="Rodelandus Arapocus">Orlandinus
                                Arapogi</name></persName> et filie quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Riccius">Ricci</name></persName>. Que est sectem stariora et
                        medietas unius panori. Et insuper (…) pretium de terra que est plus quam
                        nostra terra quod damus quatuor lib. bonorum dinariorum pisani recepimus.
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…) Actum aput <placeName
                            key="#Roads" ref="#places/3210">Puteum</placeName> in domo ospitalis.
                            (…)<persName key="#Witness #Priests">
                            <rs key="#Priests">Presbiter</rs>
                            <name ref="Lucterius">Lucterius</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Mainettus">Mainettus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bei">Bei</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Lanfrancus">Lanfrancus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ticcus">Ticcus</name></persName> filius Ricci,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bartholomaeus"
                            >Bartolomeus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Teudualdus"
                                >Tedaldini</name></persName>, suprascripti rogati <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testes</rs> interfuerunt. (S) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Hubertus"
                            >Ubertus</name></persName>, domni imperatoris <rs key="#Judge">iudex
                            ordinarius</rs> atque <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, post traditam
                        scripsi, complevi et dedi.</ab>
